

<h4 class="display-4">Upload document to sign</h4>
<hr />


<div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
    <ul>
        <li>You can upload a document <strong>for you</strong> to sign it later, but you need to <strong>generate certificate</strong> first!</li>
        <li>You can upload a document <strong>for others</strong>, if they had <strong>generated certificate!</strong></li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div asp-validation-summary="All" class="text-danger"></div>

<form method="post" asp-action="UploadUser">
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="Username" class="control-label">Upload document for username:</label>
        <input for="Username" name="Username" type="text" class="form-control" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <input type="submit" value="Upload" class="btn btn-primary" />
    </div>
</form>